title: 7 Wonders II
description: Let the mystery of 7 Wonders II blow you away! Blast stone from the game board by matching three or more relics in a row. Strategically move key building blocks down the board to the workers below before time runs out. Earn exciting power-ups and bonuses that help clear the board in fantastic fashion, and receive pieces of a hidden map, which will ultimately uncover a secret route! Come back to the unparalleled splendor that is 7 Wonders!
